[3.5, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[1;1H\u001b[3;46H\u001b[1;37mThe clock is already ticking.\u001b[0m\u001b[4;39H\u001b[2mFederal PQC compliance deadlines \u2014 CNSA 2.0\u001b[0m\u001b[7;14H\u001b[0;90m\u2503\u001b[0m\u001b[7;18H\u001b[0;90m\u001b[1m2017\u001b[0m\u001b[7;26H\u001b[0;90m\u001b[1mSHA-1 distrusted\u001b[0m\u001b[8;14H\u001b[0;90m\u2503\u001b[0m\u001b[8;26H\u001b[2mBrowsers kill SHA-1. The last easy migration.\u001b[0m"]
